sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as User Browser
    participant Envoy as Envoy Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3
    participant AuthProxy as kube-auth-proxy<br/>4180/TCP HTTP
    participant OIDC as OIDC Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant OSAuth as OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant RBACProxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Redis as Redis<br/>6379/TCP Optional TLS
    participant Upstream as Upstream App

    rect rgb(220, 240, 255)
        Note over Browser,Upstream: Flow 1: OIDC Authentication (auth mode)
        Browser->>AuthProxy: GET /oauth2/start<br/>HTTP 4180/TCP
        AuthProxy->>Browser: 302 Redirect to OIDC Provider
        Browser->>OIDC: GET /authorize<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+
        OIDC->>Browser: Login page
        Browser->>OIDC: POST credentials<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+
        OIDC->>Browser: 302 Redirect with auth code
        Browser->>AuthProxy: GET /oauth2/callback?code=...<br/>HTTP 4180/TCP
        AuthProxy->>OIDC: POST /token (code exchange)<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Client credentials
        OIDC-->>AuthProxy: Access token + ID token
        AuthProxy->>Redis: Store session (if Redis enabled)<br/>6379/TCP
        AuthProxy->>Upstream: Proxy request<br/>+ injected headers (X-Forwarded-User, etc.)
        Upstream-->>AuthProxy: Response
        AuthProxy-->>Browser: Response + Set-Cookie
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 220)
        Note over Browser,Upstream: Flow 2: Kubernetes RBAC Authorization (rbac mode)
        Browser->>RBACProxy: Request with Bearer token<br/>HTTPS 8443/TCP TLS 1.2+
        RBACProxy->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/authentication.k8s.io/v1/tokenreviews<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>RBACProxy: TokenReview result (user identity)
        RBACProxy->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/authorization.k8s.io/v1/subjectaccessreviews<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>RBACProxy: SubjectAccessReview result (allowed/denied)
        alt Authorized
            RBACProxy->>Upstream: Proxy request<br/>+ x-remote-user, x-remote-groups headers
            Upstream-->>RBACProxy: Response
            RBACProxy-->>Browser: Response
        else Denied
            RBACProxy-->>Browser: 403 Forbidden
        end
    end

    rect rgb(255, 220, 220)
        Note over Browser,Upstream: Flow 3: OpenShift OAuth Sign-Out
        Browser->>AuthProxy: GET /oauth2/sign_out<br/>HTTP 4180/TCP<br/>Session cookie
        AuthProxy->>K8sAPI: DELETE /apis/oauth.openshift.io/v1/oauthaccesstokens/{token}<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Bearer access token
        K8sAPI-->>AuthProxy: 200 OK (token deleted)
        AuthProxy-->>Browser: Clear cookie + redirect
    end

    rect rgb(220, 255, 220)
        Note over Browser,Upstream: Flow 4: Envoy ext_authz Integration (auth mode)
        Browser->>Envoy: HTTPS request<br/>443/TCP TLS 1.3
        Envoy->>AuthProxy: GET /oauth2/auth<br/>HTTP 4180/TCP<br/>Forwarded headers
        alt Authenticated (202)
            AuthProxy-->>Envoy: 202 Accepted<br/>+ auth headers
            Envoy->>Upstream: Forward request<br/>+ authenticated headers
            Upstream-->>Envoy: Response
            Envoy-->>Browser: Response
        else Not authenticated (401)
            AuthProxy-->>Envoy: 401 Unauthorized
            Envoy-->>Browser: 401 / Redirect to login
        end
    end
